Write python code for blinking LED and Traffic lights for Raspberry pi.
Solution
from gpiozero import TrafficLights
from time import sleep
lights=TrafficLights(25,8,7)
while True:
	light.green.on()
	sleep(1)
	light.amber.on()
	sleep(1)
	light.red.on()
	sleep(1)
	light.green.off()
	sleep(1)
	light.amber.off()
	sleep()
  light red.off()
